ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of JEAN-PIERRE BLAIS of Gatineau, Quebec, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of JEAN-PIERRE BLAIS to be Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission; effective June 18, 2012.
